# Exclude oversized PNG originals from Vercel deploys.
# Most PNGs in /images/ have WebP siblings that are what actually
# gets rendered. The PNG originals (some 17-27 MB each) bloat the
# deploy bundle and are never requested by browsers.
#
# This file only affects what Vercel uploads at build time. Nothing
# below is removed from the git repo.

images/*.png

# Keep logo and favicon
!images/favicon.png
!images/athlos-logo.png

# Keep PNGs referenced inline in HTML (no WebP sibling used)
!images/ufs-family-new.png
!images/ufs-cephalo-2.png
!images/wios-sensor-docking-black.png
!images/wios-award-best-product.png
!images/wios-award-dps.png

# Keep DC-Air X-ray galleries (wios.html)
!images/wios-anterior-*.png
!images/wios-posterior-*.png
!images/wios-bw-*.png

# Keep Industrial IP67 X-ray example PNGs (ufs-ip67.html)
!images/Fish*.png
!images/TwoFish*.png
!images/ChickenFillet*.png
!images/Nuts*.png
!images/Walnuts*.png
!images/Chip*.png
